                     </persName>
                     
                  , by the post from Stamford, in the county of Lincoln, directed to Messrs. Foster, Lubbock, and Co. London; containing a certain bill of exchange, numbered 3597, dated, Leicester, 21st of July 1794, signed and subscribed by one 
                     <persName id="t17950114-36-person305">
                        Edward
                         Hodges
